<?jelly escape-by-default='true'?>
<div>
    This plugin integrates <a href="https://testingbot.com">TestingBot</a> into Jenkins: it can set up and
    tear down a TestingBot Tunnel around a build, inject TestingBot credentials as environment variables, and
    embed TestingBot session reports (screenshots and video) into your JUnit test results. It supports both
    freestyle jobs and Pipeline (the <code>testingbot</code>, <code>testingbotTunnel</code> and
    <code>testingbotPublisher</code> steps).
</div>
